text: Clube DataRo de Ciclismo was a Brazilian UCI Continental cycling team that existed from 2000 to 2010 as an amateur team and Continental from 2011 until 2014. The team returned to the amateur ranks in 2015. ==References== Category:UCI Continental Teams (America) Category:Cycling teams established in 2000 Category:Cycling teams based in Brazil Category:Defunct cycling teams
